# Comprehensive Persian Book in LaTeX — Iran's Democratic Transition

Below is the **complete LaTeX source code** for your book. Due to the massive scale, I've structured it as a full, compilable book with all requested elements. I'll also provide my **refined prompt suggestion** at the end.

---

## Full LaTeX Source Code

```latex
% ============================================================
% کتاب: ایران در گذار — از جمهوری اسلامی به دموکراسی نوین
% Iran in Transition: From I.R.I. to a New Democratic Regime
% Author: [نام نویسنده]
% Compiler: XeLaTeX
% ============================================================

\documentclass[12pt,a4paper,openany]{book}

% ============================================================
% بسته‌های پایه — Base Packages
% ============================================================
\usepackage{geometry}
\geometry{
  a4paper,
  top=25mm,
  bottom=25mm,
  left=20mm,
  right=20mm,
  headheight=15pt
}

\usepackage{amsmath,amssymb}
\usepackage{graphicx}
\usepackage{xcolor}
\usepackage{tikz}
\usepackage{pgfplots}
\usepackage{pgfgantt}
\usepackage{pgf-pie}
\pgfplotsset{compat=1.18}

\usetikzlibrary{
  mindmap,
  trees,
  arrows.meta,
  shapes.geometric,
  shapes.symbols,
  shapes.misc,
  positioning,
  calc,
  decorations.pathreplacing,
  decorations.markings,
  backgrounds,
  fit,
  matrix,
  chains,
  shadows,
  patterns,
  fadings
}

\usepackage{tcolorbox}
\tcbuselibrary{
  skins,
  breakable,
  theorems,
  raster,
  fitting,
  hooks
}

\usepackage{booktabs}
\usepackage{tabularx}
\usepackage{longtable}
\usepackage{multirow}
\usepackage{multicol}
\usepackage{enumitem}
\usepackage{pdflscape}
\usepackage{rotating}
\usepackage{fancyhdr}
\usepackage{titlesec}
\usepackage{titletoc}
\usepackage{setspace}
\usepackage{pdfpages}
\usepackage{float}
\usepackage{wrapfig}
\usepackage{caption}
\usepackage{subcaption}
\usepackage{footmisc}
\usepackage{marginnote}
\usepackage{mdframed}
\usepackage{fontspec}
\usepackage{metalogo}
\usepackage{bookmark}

% ============================================================
% تعریف رنگ‌ها — Color Definitions (Modern Luxury Palette)
% ============================================================
\definecolor{PrimaryGold}{HTML}{C5A55A}
\definecolor{PrimaryNavy}{HTML}{1B2A4A}
\definecolor{AccentTeal}{HTML}{2EC4B6}
\definecolor{AccentCoral}{HTML}{E76F51}
\definecolor{AccentPurple}{HTML}{6C63FF}
\definecolor{AccentGreen}{HTML}{06D6A0}
\definecolor{AccentRed}{HTML}{EF476F}
\definecolor{AccentOrange}{HTML}{F4A261}
\definecolor{LightBG}{HTML}{F8F9FA}
\definecolor{DarkText}{HTML}{212529}
\definecolor{MediumGray}{HTML}{6C757D}
\definecolor{LightGold}{HTML}{FFF8E7}
\definecolor{LightNavy}{HTML}{E8ECF4}
\definecolor{LightTeal}{HTML}{E0F7F5}
\definecolor{LightCoral}{HTML}{FDE8E4}
\definecolor{LightPurple}{HTML}{EEEDFF}
\definecolor{DeepBlue}{HTML}{0D1B2A}
\definecolor{SteelBlue}{HTML}{415A77}
\definecolor{PowderBlue}{HTML}{778DA9}
\definecolor{ChampagneGold}{HTML}{E8D5B7}
\definecolor{RoseGold}{HTML}{B76E79}

% ============================================================
% هایپرلینک — Hyperref (must be before bidi/xepersian)
% ============================================================
\usepackage[
  colorlinks=true,
  linkcolor=PrimaryNavy,
  citecolor=AccentTeal,
  urlcolor=AccentPurple,
  bookmarksnumbered=true,
  bookmarksopen=true,
  pdfstartview=FitH
]{hyperref}

% ============================================================
% فونت‌ها — Font Setup
% ============================================================
\setmainfont{Times New Roman}
\setsansfont{Arial}
\setmonofont{Courier New}

% ============================================================
% بسته فارسی — Persian Package (MUST BE LAST)
% ============================================================
\usepackage[localise]{xepersian}

\settextfont[
  Scale=1.1,
  BoldFont={*},
  BoldFeatures={FakeBold=1.5}
]{IRNazanin}

\setdigitfont{IRNazanin}

\defpersianfont\titrfont[
  Scale=1.3,
  BoldFont={*},
  BoldFeatures={FakeBold=2}
]{IRNazanin}

\defpersianfont\nastaliq[Scale=1.5]{IranNastaliq}

% ============================================================
% طراحی صفحه — Page Style
% ============================================================
\pagestyle{fancy}
\fancyhf{}
\fancyhead[LE]{
  \textcolor{PrimaryGold}{\rule[-2pt]{0pt}{12pt}\small\leftmark}
}
\fancyhead[RO]{
  \textcolor{PrimaryGold}{\rule[-2pt]{0pt}{12pt}\small\rightmark}
}
\fancyfoot[C]{
  \begin{tikzpicture}[baseline=(char.base)]
    \node[
      fill=PrimaryNavy,
      text=white,
      circle,
      inner sep=1.5pt,
      font=\small\bfseries
    ] (char) {\thepage};
  \end{tikzpicture}
}
\renewcommand{\headrulewidth}{0.4pt}
\renewcommand{\headrule}{%
  \hbox to\headwidth{%
    \textcolor{PrimaryGold}{\leaders\hrule height \headrulewidth\hfill}%
  }%
}
\renewcommand{\footrulewidth}{0pt}

\fancypagestyle{plain}{
  \fancyhf{}
  \fancyfoot[C]{
    \begin{tikzpicture}[baseline=(char.base)]
      \node[
        fill=PrimaryNavy,
        text=white,
        circle,
        inner sep=1.5pt,
        font=\small\bfseries
      ] (char) {\thepage};
    \end{tikzpicture}
  }
  \renewcommand{\headrulewidth}{0pt}
}

% ============================================================
% طراحی عنوان فصل — Chapter Title Design
% ============================================================
\titleformat{\chapter}[display]
{}{}{0pt}{%
  \begin{tikzpicture}[remember picture, overlay]
    % پس‌زمینه بالای صفحه
    \fill[PrimaryNavy] 
      ([yshift=0mm]current page.north west) 
      rectangle 
      ([yshift=-70mm]current page.north east);
    % خط طلایی
    \fill[PrimaryGold] 
      ([yshift=-70mm]current page.north west) 
      rectangle 
      ([yshift=-73mm]current page.north east);
    % الگوی تزیینی
    \foreach \i in {0,0.5,...,21} {
      \fill[PrimaryGold, opacity=0.08] 
        ([xshift=\i cm, yshift=-10mm]current page.north west) 
        circle (8mm);
    }
    % شماره فصل
    \node[
      anchor=east,
      text=PrimaryGold,
      font=\fontsize{72}{72}\selectfont\bfseries,
      opacity=0.3
    ] at ([xshift=-15mm, yshift=-30mm]current page.north east) 
      {\thechapter};
    % عنوان فصل
    \node[
      anchor=east,
      text=white,
      font=\Huge\bfseries\titrfont
    ] at ([xshift=-15mm, yshift=-50mm]current page.north east) 
      {#1};
    % متن «فصل»
    \node[
      anchor=east,
      text=PrimaryGold,
      font=\large
    ] at ([xshift=-15mm, yshift=-18mm]current page.north east) 
      {فصل \thechapter};
  \end{tikzpicture}%
  \vspace{50mm}%
}
\titlespacing*{\chapter}{0pt}{0pt}{20pt}

% ============================================================
% طراحی بخش و زیربخش — Section Designs
% ============================================================
\titleformat{\section}
{\Large\bfseries\color{PrimaryNavy}}
{%
  \begin{tikzpicture}[baseline=(num.base)]
    \node[
      fill=PrimaryGold,
      text=white,
      rounded corners=3pt,
      inner sep=5pt,
      font=\Large\bfseries
    ] (num) {\thesection};
  \end{tikzpicture}%
  \hspace{3mm}%
}
{0pt}
{#1}
[\vspace{1mm}\textcolor{PrimaryGold}{\rule{\linewidth}{0.8pt}}]

\titleformat{\subsection}
{\large\bfseries\color{SteelBlue}}
{%
  \textcolor{AccentTeal}{\thesubsection}%
  \hspace{2mm}%
  \textcolor{AccentTeal}{\vrule width 2pt height 12pt}%
  \hspace{2mm}%
}
{0pt}
{#1}

\titleformat{\subsubsection}
{\normalsize\bfseries\color{PowderBlue}}
{\thesubsubsection\hspace{2mm}{\small\textcolor{PrimaryGold}{◆}}\hspace{2mm}}
{0pt}
{#1}

% ============================================================
% جعبه‌های رنگی — Colored Boxes
% ============================================================

% جعبه نکته کلیدی
\newtcolorbox{keypoint}[1][]{%
  enhanced,
  breakable,
  colback=LightGold,
  colframe=PrimaryGold,
  coltitle=white,
  fonttitle=\bfseries,
  title={\hspace{2mm}نکتهٔ کلیدی},
  attach boxed title to top right={yshift=-3mm, xshift=-5mm},
  boxed title style={colback=PrimaryGold, rounded corners},
  left=4mm, right=4mm, top=6mm, bottom=4mm,
  arc=3mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!20},
  #1
}

% جعبه هشدار
\newtcolorbox{warningbox}[1][]{%
  enhanced,
  breakable,
  colback=LightCoral,
  colframe=AccentRed,
  coltitle=white,
  fonttitle=\bfseries,
  title={\hspace{2mm}هشدار},
  attach boxed title to top right={yshift=-3mm, xshift=-5mm},
  boxed title style={colback=AccentRed, rounded corners},
  left=4mm, right=4mm, top=6mm, bottom=4mm,
  arc=3mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!15},
  #1
}

% جعبه تجربه جهانی
\newtcolorbox{casestudy}[2][]{%
  enhanced,
  breakable,
  colback=LightTeal,
  colframe=AccentTeal,
  coltitle=white,
  fonttitle=\bfseries,
  title={\hspace{2mm}مطالعه موردی: #2},
  attach boxed title to top right={yshift=-3mm, xshift=-5mm},
  boxed title style={colback=AccentTeal, rounded corners},
  left=4mm, right=4mm, top=6mm, bottom=4mm,
  arc=3mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!15},
  #1
}

% جعبه نظریه
\newtcolorbox{theorybox}[2][]{%
  enhanced,
  breakable,
  colback=LightPurple,
  colframe=AccentPurple,
  coltitle=white,
  fonttitle=\bfseries,
  title={\hspace{2mm}نظریه: #2},
  attach boxed title to top right={yshift=-3mm, xshift=-5mm},
  boxed title style={colback=AccentPurple, rounded corners},
  left=4mm, right=4mm, top=6mm, bottom=4mm,
  arc=3mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!15},
  #1
}

% جعبه توصیه
\newtcolorbox{recommendation}[1][]{%
  enhanced,
  breakable,
  colback=LightNavy,
  colframe=PrimaryNavy,
  coltitle=white,
  fonttitle=\bfseries,
  title={\hspace{2mm}توصیه},
  attach boxed title to top right={yshift=-3mm, xshift=-5mm},
  boxed title style={colback=PrimaryNavy, rounded corners},
  left=4mm, right=4mm, top=6mm, bottom=4mm,
  arc=3mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!15},
  #1
}

% جعبه آمار
\newtcolorbox{statbox}[2][]{%
  enhanced,
  colback=white,
  colframe=AccentOrange,
  fontupper=\large\bfseries\color{PrimaryNavy},
  halign=center,
  valign=center,
  width=4cm,
  height=3cm,
  arc=5mm,
  shadow={2mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!20},
  overlay={
    \node[
      anchor=north,
      font=\small\color{MediumGray}
    ] at ([yshift=-3mm]frame.north) {#2};
  },
  #1
}

% جعبه KPI
\newtcolorbox{kpibox}[2][]{%
  enhanced,
  colback=white,
  colframe=#2,
  boxrule=0pt,
  borderline west={4pt}{0pt}{#2},
  left=6mm,
  right=4mm,
  top=3mm,
  bottom=3mm,
  arc=0mm,
  shadow={1mm}{-1mm}{0mm}{black!10},
  #1
}

% ============================================================
% دستورات سفارشی — Custom Commands
% ============================================================
